# Changelog

## [Core v1.1.17] – 2025-10-25
- Immutable mathematical foundation consolidated.
- Added 1-Lipschitz constraint to Vantage-Swap Invariance.
- Explicit normalization and index-set expectations.
- COHERENCE_REPAIR steps formalized.
- Metrics clipped to [0, 1].

## [Instructions v1.1.17] – 2025-10-25
- Plain-language interface.
- Default mode: natural conversation; formal TSC mode on request.
- Added “See-more” handler and structured output format.
